      <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;The church that teaches critical thinking.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Belief in god is not the problem. Belief without evidence is the
problem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The more certain you are, the closer you are to the dangerous edge
of orthodoxy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you think you have the truth, you stop looking. When you stop
looking, you no longer see. It&#39;s best not to be blinded by
complacency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
